Package: scrapeR
Type: Package
Title: The \code{scraper} Function Fetches and Extracts Text Content from Specified Web Pages and Handles HTTP Errors and Parses HTML Efficiently
Version: 0.1.7
Author: Mathieu Dubeau, Ph.D
Maintainer: Mathieu Dubeau <mdubeau20@gmail.com>
Description: The \code{scrapeR} function fetches and extracts text content from specified web pages. It handles HTTP errors and parses HTML efficiently. The function can handle hundreds of websites at a time using the 'in_batches' command.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports: 
    httr,
    rvest,
    utils,
    magrittr

